{
  "description": "Keyword rubric mapping roll-call votes to democratic-institution impact scores (1-5). Matched case-insensitively against bill number + question + subject. The HIGHEST severity among matched domains wins; unmatched votes default to impact 1 (routine policy). Edit freely - the scorer and dashboard pick changes up on the next run.",
